{"id":349,"date":"2022-05-29T06:43:33","date_gmt":"2022-05-29T06:43:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/?p=349"},"modified":"2025-02-24T11:47:05","modified_gmt":"2025-02-24T11:47:05","slug":"mahjong-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Mahjong L\u00e0 G\u00ec? C\u00e1ch Ch\u01a1i Mahjong Tr\u00ean Sv368 Chu\u1ea9n Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hoa"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#Mahjong_la_gi\" >Mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#Luat_choi_mahjong_de_hieu_nhat\" >Lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i mahjong d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea5t<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#Muc_dich\" >M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#So_nguoi_choi\" >S\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#Chia_bai\" >Chia b\u00e0i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#Xep_bai\" >X\u1ebfp b\u00e0i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#Ra_bai\" >Ra b\u00e0i<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/#Huong_dan_cach_choi_mahjong_chuan_nguoi_Hoa\" >H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i mahjong chu\u1ea9n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hoa<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\r\n<p><strong>Mahjong hay m\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hoa. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi nh\u1edb, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c ngay khi v\u1eeba b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1eady mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec, c\u00f3 kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">SV368 <\/a>t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i mahjong chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c sau \u0111\u00e2y.<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111ang xem : <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/mahjong-la-gi\/\">Mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec ?<\/a><\/p>\r\n<\/blockquote>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mahjong_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>Mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Mahjong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u00ean m\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u1ee3c khi du nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Trong m\u1ed7i v\u00e1n ch\u01a1i, b\u1ea1n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 Thanh, Trung Qu\u1ed1c. M\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u1ee3c trong ti\u1ebfng Qu\u1ea3ng \u0110\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 con chim s\u1ebb v\u1eebng (ma t\u01b0\u1edbc). C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 do qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chim s\u1ebb l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i m\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u1ee3c (nh\u1ea5t s\u00e1ch) n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\">\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_2699\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2699\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2699 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-1-2.jpg\" alt=\"Mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-1-2.jpg?v=1708422741 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-1-2-300x150.jpg?v=1708422741 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-1-2-768x384.jpg?v=1708422741 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2699\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Mahjong v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1975 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 d\u00e0nh cho t\u1ea7ng l\u1edbp th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecba v\u1ecb, quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c. Th\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ea1c ch\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u1ecb th\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u00e0u c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau th\u00edch.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\">\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; Xem th\u00eam :<a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-chan-gioi\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-choi-chan-gioi\/\"> c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafn gi\u1ecfi<\/a><\/em><\/p>\r\n<\/blockquote>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Luat_choi_mahjong_de_hieu_nhat\"><\/span><strong>Lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i mahjong d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u nh\u1ea5t<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm r\u00f5 lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eadt m\u00ed ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Muc_dich\"><\/span><strong>M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi T\u1edbi hay \u00d9, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fac b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f2n b\u00e0i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp th\u00e0nh 4 nh\u00f3m v\u00e0 1 \u0111\u00f4i. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n 13 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f2n b\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 1 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u00e0i \u00d9.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"So_nguoi_choi\"><\/span><strong>S\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>M\u1ed7i v\u00e1n mahjong th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn gi\u00f3 Trung, nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf gi\u00f3 \u0110\u00f4ng khi \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft v\u00f2ng gi\u00f3. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 6 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, gi\u1eef gi\u00f3 Trung v\u00e0 gi\u00f3 Ph\u00e1t. 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia ch\u01a1i khi h\u1ebft gi\u00f3 \u0110\u00f4ng v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng v\u00e0 T\u00e2y.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\">\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_2700\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2700\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2700\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-2-2.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e1n mahjong\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-2-2.jpg?v=1708422742 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-2-2-300x150.jpg?v=1708422742 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-2-2-768x384.jpg?v=1708422742 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2700\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e1n mahjong<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>V\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c tung x\u00fac x\u1eafc. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y 4 qu\u00e2n \u0110\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Nam B\u1eafc ra xoa, r\u1ed3i x\u1ebfp ch\u1ed3ng l\u00ean nhau ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean. Sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u00e3y gieo 2 vi\u00ean x\u00fac x\u1eafc. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi cao \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y qu\u00e2n tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p d\u1ea7n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e2n \u0110\u00f4ng (c\u1eeda \u0110\u00f4ng) c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\r\n<p>C\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi sau l\u1ea5y c\u1eeda \u0110\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i.Ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn c\u1eeda \u0110\u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i \u1edf v\u00e1n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u00f2n c\u00e1c v\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp theo th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o \u00f9 s\u1ebd l\u00e0m c\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi chuy\u1ebfn h\u01b0\u1edfng sang tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef c\u1eeda \u0110\u00f4ng.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chia_bai\"><\/span><strong>Chia b\u00e0i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Khi chia b\u00e0i, c\u00e1c qu\u00e2n mahjong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fap xu\u1ed1ng, r\u1ed3i x\u00e1o l\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp ch\u00fang th\u00e0nh 2 h\u00e0ng ngang nh\u01b0ng \u00fap ch\u1ed3ng l\u00ean nhau v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 qu\u00e2n ngang nhau. Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ebfp xong th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea9y 2 h\u00e0ng b\u00e0i l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i s\u1ebd tung 2 &#8211; 3 vi\u00ean x\u00fac x\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec3m chia b\u00e0i. Sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfm b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i theo chi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i sang ph\u1ea3i.<\/p>\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ed5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x l\u1ea7n th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfm x s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1eeda b\u1ecb l\u1ea5y b\u00e0i. Qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n th\u1ee9 x+1 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i sang ph\u1ea3i. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m c\u00e1i s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1eeda ti\u1ebfp theo c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i sang. Sau 3 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd s\u1edf h\u1eefu 12 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i, r\u1ed3i m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i, c\u00f2n c\u1eeda \u0110\u00f4ng th\u00ec l\u1ea5y hai qu\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu c\u1eeda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea1n b\u00e0i th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd l\u1ea5y b\u00e0i \u1edf c\u1eeda k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\">\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_2701\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2701\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2701\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-3-2.jpg\" alt=\"Chia b\u00e0i trong 1 v\u00e1n m\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o x\u00fac x\u1eafc\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-3-2.jpg?v=1708422743 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-3-2-300x150.jpg?v=1708422743 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-3-2-768x384.jpg?v=1708422743 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2701\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Chia b\u00e0i trong 1 v\u00e1n m\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o x\u00fac x\u1eafc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xep_bai\"><\/span><strong>X\u1ebfp b\u00e0i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00ec lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a game n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, ngay c\u1ea3 c\u00e1ch x\u1ebfp b\u00e0i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n theo m\u1ed9t quy lu\u1eadt ri\u00eang. Quy t\u1eafc l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i c\u00f3 hoa, c\u00f3 khung hay coong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp b\u00ean tr\u00e1i, c\u00f2n qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1c l\u00ean x\u1ebfp b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00e1c qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c tay b\u00e0i nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0 phu, m\u1eaft, trong \u0111\u00f3 1 phu c\u00f3 3 qu\u00e2n, c\u00f3 4 ph\u00fat trong m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9; 1 m\u1eaft l\u00e0 1 qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p m\u1ea5t khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh x\u1ebfp b\u00e0i. Phu ngang hay phu d\u1ecdc th\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1i.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ra_bai\"><\/span><strong>Ra b\u00e0i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i s\u1ebd s\u1edf h\u1eefu 14 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Khi c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra b\u00e0i th\u00ec nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0103n qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh phu ph\u1ed7ng. C\u1eeda c\u00e1i khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n hoa th\u00ec c\u00f3 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh qu\u00e2n hoa v\u00e0 d\u1ef1ng qu\u00e2n hoa, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 qu\u00e2n hoa th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1ng l\u00ean. Khi d\u1ef1ng hoa l\u00ean th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n b\u1eaft qu\u00e2n ch\u1ed3ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 coong. M\u1ed7i qu\u00e2n hoa nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi b\u1eaft m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Khi nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i ra qu\u00e2n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i n\u00e0o ph\u1ed7ng th\u00ec s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i \u1edf ch\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfp m\u1ed9t qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t ra b\u00e0i \u1edf m\u1ed7i c\u1eeda kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi b\u1ea1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi c\u00f3 ai \u0111\u00f3 \u00d9.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\">\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_2702\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2702\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2702 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-4.jpg\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd ra b\u00e0i cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00f9 b\u00e0i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-4.jpg?v=1708422744 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-4-300x150.jpg?v=1708422744 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/hinh-4-768x384.jpg?v=1708422744 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2702\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i s\u1ebd ra b\u00e0i cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00f9 b\u00e0i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\r\n<\/figure>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_cach_choi_mahjong_chuan_nguoi_Hoa\"><\/span><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i mahjong chu\u1ea9n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hoa<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i ra b\u00e0i th\u00ec nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i chi\u1ebfu b\u00e0i m\u00ecnh xem c\u00f3 \u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hay kh\u00f4ng. M\u1ed7i v\u00e1n mahjong s\u1ebd g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 4 l\u01b0\u1ee3t gi\u00f3, \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi gi\u00f3 \u0110\u00f4ng, T\u00e2y, Nam B\u1eafc. M\u1ed7i l\u01b0\u1ee3t gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u1eeda t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi gi\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>M\u1ed7i v\u00e1n mahjong s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac khi c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1edbi b\u00e0i (\u00d9 b\u00e0i). B\u1ed9 b\u00e0i l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m tr\u00f2n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p sau:<\/strong><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>1 \u0111\u00f4i g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 2 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ed1ng nhau.<\/li>\r\n<li>1 ph\u1ed7ng (phu ngang) g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 3 qu\u00e2n gi\u1ed1ng nhau, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c b\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c \u0103n b\u00e0i.<\/li>\r\n<li>1 ph\u00ecnh (phu d\u1ecdc) s\u1ebd g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 3 qu\u00e2n x\u1ebfp theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1.<\/li>\r\n<li>T\u00e0i phao ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ph\u1ed7ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n.<\/li>\r\n<li>Chi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 3 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i v\u00e0 thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e2n th\u1ee9 4 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c b\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c \u0103n b\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i chu\u1ea9n t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hoa. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i th\u1eafng Mahjong n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. H\u00e3y quan s\u00e1t v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb c\u00e1c cao th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ea5n th\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u00e9.<\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Mahjong hay m\u1ea1t ch\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00fa v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hoa. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi nh\u1edb, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c ngay khi v\u1eeba b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1eady mahjong l\u00e0 g\u00ec, c\u00f3 kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng SV368 t\u00ecm [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[8],"tags":[24,23],"class_list":["post-349","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-game-bai","tag-game-bai-sv368","tag-mahjong-la-gi"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/349","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=349"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/349\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5711,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/349\/revisions\/5711"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=349"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=349"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=349"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}